    {
      "Text": "Security update for gnutls",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for gnutls fixes the following issues:\n\n- CVE-2025-14831: Fixed DoS via excessive resource consumption during certificate verification. (bsc#1257960)\n- Add the functionality to allow to specify the hash algorithm for the PSK. This fixes a bug in the current implementation where the binder is always calculated with SHA256. (bsc#1258083, jsc#PED-15752, jsc#PED-15753)\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
    },
